{UTF-8}
Crew Size=4 + STEP(4, 15)
	~	People
	~		|

Metabolic Consumption Rate=Crew Size * Oxygen per Person
	~	kg/Day
	~		|

O2 Generation Rate=5
	~	kg/Day
	~		|

Oxygen per Person=0.84
	~	kg/Day/Person
	~		|

Oxygen Reserve= INTEG (O2 Generation Rate-Metabolic Consumption Rate,
		500)
	~	kg
	~		|

Recycled Water Stock= INTEG (Water Recovery Rate - (Crew Size * 2),
		1000)
	~	Liters
	~		|

Water Recovery Rate=(Crew Size * 2) * 0.9
	~	Liters/Day
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
		Simulation Control Parameters
	|

FINAL TIME  = 30
	~	Day
	~	The final time for the simulation.
	|

INITIAL TIME  = 0
	~	Day
	~	The initial time for the simulation.
	|

SAVEPER  = 
        TIME STEP 
	~	Day [0,?]
	~	The frequency with which output is stored.
	|

TIME STEP  = 0.25
	~	Day [0,?]
	~	The time step for the simulation.
	|

